flowchart TD
    Start([User submits query]) --> Validate
    Validate -->|valid| Process[QAService.answer_query]
    Process --> UseLLM{useLLM?}
    UseLLM -->|No| Retrieve[Engine.search → articles]
    Retrieve --> Return[Return articles only]
    UseLLM -->|Yes| CheckOllama{Ollama reachable?}
    CheckOllama -->|No| Retrieve
    CheckOllama -->|Yes| CheckModel{Model available?}
    CheckModel -->|No| Retrieve --> ReturnWithStatus[Return articles + warning]
    CheckModel -->|Yes| RagFull[RAGWorkflow.ask: retrieve + LLM]
    RagFull --> LLMCall[Ollama generates answer]
    LLMCall --> ReturnFull[Return answer + articles]
    ReturnFull --> End([Response sent])
    Return --> End
    ReturnWithStatus --> End